<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CS Education Hub | 计算机科教展示</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        .glass-card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">

    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-slate-200 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex justify-between h-16 items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i data-lucide="cpu" class="text-blue-600"></i>
                    <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">CS Exhibit</span>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm font-medium">
                    <a href=" " class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">首页</a >
                    <a href="#video" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">视频教程</a >
                    <a href="#docs" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">学习文档</a >
                    <a href="#about" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">关于</a >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header id="home" class="relative py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-indigo-700 text-white text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6">探索计算机科学的奥秘</h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-100 mb-10">这里汇集了前沿的 CS 教学资源、精选视频与深度文档，助你从入门到精通。</p >
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="#video" class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-blue-50 transition">开始学习</a >
                <a href="#docs" class="border border-white/30 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition">查看文档</a >
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        
        <section id="video" class="mb-20">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
                <i data-lucide="play-circle" class="text-blue-600"></i>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">精选视频展示</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-black rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-video relative group">
                    <iframe id="mainPlayer" class="w-full h-full" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">课程目录</h3>
                    <button onclick="changeVideo('https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ')" class="w-full flex items-center p-3 gap-4 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 text-left hover:bg-blue-100 transition">
                        <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm">01</span>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-sm font-medium">计算机组成原理概览</div>
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="changeVideo('https://www.youtube.com/embed/example2')" class="w-full flex items-center p-3 gap-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200 text-left hover:border-blue-300 transition">
                        <span class="bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm">02</span>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-sm font-medium">数据结构：树与图的遍历</div>
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="changeVideo('https://www.youtube.com/embed/example3')" class="w-full flex items-center p-3 gap-4 rounded-xl bg-white border border-slate-200 text-left hover:border-blue-300 transition">
                        <span class="bg-slate-200 text-slate-600 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm">03</span>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-sm font-medium">操作系统：内存管理深度解析</div>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="docs" class="mb-20">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
                <i data-lucide="file-text" class="text-blue-600"></i>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">学习文档 & 讲义</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="file-type"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">课程大纲.pdf</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">包含了整个学期的教学安排与重点考察内容。</p >
                    <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline">
                        下载文档 <i data-lucide="download" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </a >
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="code"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">实验指导书.zip</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">包含所有 Python/C++ 实验的源码模板与说明。</p >
                    <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline">
                        下载源码 <i data-lucide="download" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </a >
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="layers"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">期末复习思维导图</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">一张图理清整个学科的核心逻辑架构。</p >
                    <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline">
                        在线预览 <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </a >
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition duration-300">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl mb-4">
                        <i data-lucide="book-open"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">扩展阅读列表</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">教授推荐的 10 本必读经典计算机书籍。</p >
                    <a href="#" class="text-blue-600 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline">
                        查看列表 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    </a >
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer id="about" class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mb-4 text-white">
                <i data-lucide="github"></i>
                <span class="font-bold">CS Education Project</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm">© 2024 由您的名字驱动 - 基于 GitHub Pages 构建</p >
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // 初始化图标
        lucide.createIcons();

        // 切换视频功能
        function changeVideo(url) {
            document.getElementById('mainPlayer').src = url;
            // 可以在这里添加代码来改变按钮的高亮状态
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
